Placeholder Recurring Encounter

Something happens! In the scary plains.

choices:

* Negotiate = Try to convince them
    @if check negotiation hard {
      You convince them!
      +heal_spirits 3
      +give_gold 3
      +repool
    } @else {
      You fail!
      +rem_gold 3
      +damage_spirits 3
      +repool
    }

* Fight = Do the ultimate punchies
    @if check combat medium {
        You win!
        +heal_spirits 3
        +give_gold 3
        +repool
    } @else {
        You lose!
        +add_condition injured
        +damage_spirits 3
        +repool
    }

* Sneak = Use big sneaky skills
    @if check cunning medium {
        You win!
        +heal_spirits 3
        +give_gold 3
        +repool
    } @else {
        You lose!
        +add_condition injured
        +damage_spirits 3
        +repool
    }
